[h2][b]Suru++[/b][/h2]
[h4][b]A third-party Suru icons for Ubuntu 18.04
An elegant, modern and sweet Suru icons based on Suru Icons by Sam Hewitt[/b][/h4]

[h4][b]ATTENTION[/b][/h4]

[b]DO NOT[/b] report bugs to me! Report ONLY to Gustavo Costa (gusreis1989) [b] at Github.[/b]
[b]PLEASE UNDERSTAND[/b] that I am [b]NOT[/b] a developer. I am [b]ONLY a designer. [b]PLEASE RESPECT[/b] me and my limit. [b]DO NOT[/b] overload me with these things.
I [b]DO NOT[/b] work with dark icons themes and other icons themes. ONLY Gustavo works with it. 

We invite you to answer the polls about Suru++ repositories ownerships because we analysed and observe the statistics of our repositories and our pages, we have doubts with you:
